snippet.title: Starship Troopers: Extermination Gameplay Update Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Team members from Offworld Industries swung by the Future Games Show at Gamescom to reveal more about the Tanker Bug and a new frosty biome coming to Starship Troopers: Extermination. It's coming to consoles on October 11th, 2024, but it's already available in early access on PC.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow
